    "Keep 127.0.0.1 unless you intentionally expose the legacy HTTP API on your LAN." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "除非你明确要在局域网暴露旧 HTTP API，否则保持 127.0.0.1。" } } }
    },
    "Kept for Stage 3 rollback and compatibility only. New setup should use the Swift service and bundled Swift stdio MCP helper." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "仅为 Stage 3 回滚和兼容保留。新配置应使用 Swift 服务和随附的 Swift stdio MCP helper。" } } }
    },
