    "Periodically refresh" : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "定期刷新" } } }
    },
    "Preset" : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "预设" } } }
    },
    "Primary runtime for the macOS app. Settings, search, indexing, and operational actions should use Swift service IPC during Stage 3." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "macOS 应用的主运行时。Stage 3 期间，设置、搜索、索引和运维操作都应使用 Swift 服务 IPC。" } } }
    },
    "Primary setup: point MCP clients directly at the bundled Swift stdio helper. Mutating tools use Swift service IPC and fail closed when the service is unavailable." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "主配置：让 MCP 客户端直接指向随附的 Swift stdio helper。变更类工具使用 Swift 服务 IPC，服务不可用时失败关闭。" } } }
    },
    "Required" : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "必填" } } }
    },
    "These are low-level filters behind the simplified Session Filter control." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "这些是简化版会话过滤控件背后的底层过滤项。" } } }
    },
    "These sessions have no messages and clutter search results. Hidden sessions are not deleted — view them again under Sessions → Show hidden sessions." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "这些会话没有任何消息，会扰乱搜索结果。隐藏不会删除它们——你仍可在 会话 → 显示已隐藏会话 中再次查看。" } } }
    },
    "These settings power semantic search and memory. Changing model or dimension may require rebuilding vector indexes." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "这些设置用于语义搜索和记忆。更改模型或维度后，可能需要重建向量索引。" } } }
    },
    "Toggle theme: System → Light → Dark" : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "切换主题：系统 → 浅色 → 深色" } } }
    },
    "USD" : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "美元" } } }
    },
    "Version" : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "版本" } } }
    },
    "Project migration tools always require the Swift service. When on, remaining MCP write tools such as save_insight also fail if the Swift service can't be reached, instead of falling back to a direct DB write. Takes effect on the next Swift MCP spawn." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "项目迁移工具始终需要 Swift 服务。开启后，save_insight 等其余 MCP 写入工具在无法连接 Swift 服务时也会失败，而不是回退到直接写数据库。下次启动 Swift MCP 时生效。" } } }
    },
    "When on, MCP write tools (save_insight, project_move, …) fail if the Swift service can't be reached, instead of falling back to a direct DB write. Reduces lock contention to zero; requires the service IPC socket. Takes effect on the next Swift MCP spawn." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "开启后，MCP 写入工具（save_insight、project_move 等）在无法连接 Swift 服务时会失败，而不是回退到直接写数据库。这样可将锁竞争降为零；需要服务 IPC socket。下次启动 Swift MCP 时生效。" } } }
    },
    "Write APIs should use a bearer token when HTTP is reachable beyond localhost." : {
      "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "当 HTTP 可从 localhost 之外访问时，写入 API 应使用 bearer token。" } } }
